title: BMW stolen from Elante Mall parking lot
text:
Tribune News Service
Chandigarh, October 2
A BMW car was stolen from a parking lot outside the Elante Mall, on October 1. The police said Gagandeep Singh, a resident of Kalenganupur village, Amritsar, complained he had visited the mall with his friends. Police sources said when the complainant returned he found that the luxury car that he had come in was missing from the parking lot. A case of theft has been registered at the Industrial Area police station and a probe has been initiated.
